Bootcamp Project 1

Objective

The objective of Day 3 was to clean, validate, and transform Bronze data into Silver Parquet datasets using Azure Data Factory Mapping Data Flows.

Data Flows Created
- df_clean_customers
- df_clean_products
- df_clean_product_category
- df_clean_orders
- df_clean_sales

Transformations Implemented
- Null validation
- Primary key validation
- Duplicate removal
- Data type conversion
- Column filtering
- CSV to Parquet conversion

Silver Outputs Generated
- Silver Layer Datasets
 - silver/customers
 - silver/products
 - silver/product_category
 - silver/orders
 - silver/sales

Outputs were generated in compressed Parquet format.

Validation Performed
- Row count validation
- Output verification
- Pipeline validation
- Monitor validation

Key Learnings
- ADF Mapping Data Flows
- Spark-based transformations
- Parquet optimization
- Data validation techniques
- Silver layer processing
